data.description: Buyers financing fell through. This charming house is now available for sale. With 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this property is perfect for those seeking a cozy yet spacious home. Some of the highlights of this house is the completely renovated kitchen, new flooring, 2023 HVAC, and fresh paint through out. The kitchen was renovated in 2020 with all new cabinets, a stylish backsplash, a modern sink, and newer appliances, providing a fresh and contemporary look. The majority of the house features beautiful flooring that adds both elegance and durability to the space. Additionally, two of the bedrooms have plush carpeting, providing comfort and warmth. Step outside onto the new concrete patio, where you can enjoy outdoor gatherings or simply relax in the fresh air. This outdoor space offers endless possibilities for creating your own oasis.
